<p>For example I have this estructure:</p>  <pre><code>- App    - Pod1    - Pod2 </code></pre>  <p><code>Pod1</code> calls <code>Pod2</code>, after that <code>Pod2</code> needs to get the <code>Pod1</code>'s bundle. </p>  <p>If I call <code>[NSBundle mainBundle]</code> in <code>Pod2</code> the bundle that I get is the App bundle.</p>  <p>How can I get the <code>Pod1</code>'s bundle from <code>Pod2</code>?</p>